name: The 2012 Windsurfing Calendar - UK SHIPPING
description:
Presenting the 2012 Windsurfing Calendar: 

We’ve teamed up with the inimitable John Carter and the guys at +27 design agency to put together what we reckon to be a pretty damn inspiring calendar to brighten up your wall for 2012.

Featuring 15 of JC’s favorite images from the past year (and a vintage Naish shot for good measure), and including a sexy untouched full-bleed final image to adorn your wall when 2012 draws to a close, we guarantee you won’t be disappointed.

Click on the thumbnails (there's more images in the other shipping options) for a peek inside, or hit ‘add to cart’ to bag yours.
 
Spec:
Size: A3 Portrait
Style: Ring bound, full flip A3.
Pages: 15 (front cover, 12 months, about the photographer, full bleed).
Riders: Robby Naish, Jason Polakow, Marcilio Brown, Levi Siver, Scott McKercher, Philip Koster, Victor Fernandez, Chris Murray, Boujmaa Guilloul, Camille Juban, Ricardo Campello, Robby Swift and Kevin Pritchard.
Locations: Maui, Cape Town, Western Australia.
Price: £19.95 +p&p.
